          "reviewBody": "The School Staff is very rude and even the principal of the school is very very rude. She even doesn't know how to speak with the  parents. The other management staffs are also very rude and don't know how to behave with the parents and talk respectfully.\n\nAbove all the school infrastructure is pathetic and they don't even care of the small kids. They made small kids sit under a tent without fan, water or even access to clean toilets in scorching heat for more than 6 hours.",
          "publisher": {
